00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:18.160
But when we do that, we experience what Psalm 1 verse 2 says.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:28.160
His delight is in the law of Jehovah, and he reads his law in an undertone day and night.

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:33.160
