00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:35.159
It promotes creative thinking.

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:39.159
We marvel at Jehovah's love and wisdom.

00:08:39.159 --> 00:08:44.159
Not only has He given us life and the means to sustain it,

00:08:44.159 --> 00:08:49.159
but He has also given us the ability to find pleasure in doing so.

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:57.500
